hs125

If you are still using cycle 1015 and 1016, then you need to adjust your clock (time zone) to a country that has DST (Daylight Saving Time).  From there, you can access jeppview.  But, if you already downloaded and installed cycle 1017, then there is no need to adjust the clock to DST.
Jeppview will work without adjusting the clock to DST.
